+## Review Reply Draft
+
+### T-214-01
+Addressed in `src/policy/preview.py` and `src/policy/approval_router.py`.
+The fallback payload now preserves `approval_state` and
+`requires_human_review`, and the router normalizes `manual_review` to
+`human_review_required` before building either live or fallback preview
+responses.
+
+### T-214-02
+Marked duplicate of `T-214-01`.
+The reported issue is the same reopened fallback regression, so no separate code
+change was applied for this thread.
+
+### T-214-03
+Marked obsolete.
+The comment points at an outdated diff hunk and suggests reviving legacy preview
+branching on the current branch. That change was intentionally not applied.
+
+### T-214-04
+Addressed in `tests/test_preview.py`.
+Added a regression test covering `preview_enabled=False` with
+`approval_state="manual_review"` to verify the payload keeps
+`approval_state="human_review_required"` and `requires_human_review=true`.
+
+### T-214-05
+Addressed in `docs/approval_policy.md`.
+Updated the fallback example so it matches the corrected payload and includes
+the human review fields.
